Spring lightup this evening at Kiyomizudera Temple.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
今晩、清水寺で春のライトアップ。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Lightup" /><category term="Kiyomizudera" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><summary type="html">Spring lightup this evening at Kiyomizudera Temple.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2104_A7R04638-E.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Petals in the Water・水中の花びら</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210331/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Petals in the Water・水中の花びら" /><published>2021-03-31T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-31T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/nanatanigawa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210331/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
