&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
亀岡市七谷川さくら公園では、何千枚もの桜の花びらが川を下って流れます。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Rivers" /><summary type="html">It’s the beginning of the end of the cherry blossom season, as thousands of petals flow down the river at Nanatani River Sakura Park in Kameoka.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R04549.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Philosopher’s Path・哲学の道</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210330/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Philosopher's Path・哲学の道" /><published>2021-03-30T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-30T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/tetsugaku</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210330/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
