&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
十石船は伏見の酒蔵地区にある桜並木の運河を走ります。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Boats" /><summary type="html">A Jikkokubune boat travels along a canal lined with cherry blossoms in the Fushimi Sake district.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R04272.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Daigo-ji Temple・醍醐寺</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210328/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Daigo-ji Temple・醍醐寺" /><published>2021-03-28T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-28T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/daigoji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210328/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
The Bentendo Temple and bridge at Daigo-ji Temple.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
醍醐寺の弁天堂と橋。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html">The Bentendo Temple and bridge at Daigo-ji Temple.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R04211.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Spring on the River・大堰川の春</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210327/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Spring on the River・大堰川の春" /><published>2021-03-27T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-27T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/oigawa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210327/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Beautiful day for taking a ride on the Katsura (Oi) River to watch the cherry blossoms.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
船に乗って桜を眺めるには絶好の日和です。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Boats" /><category term="Katsura River" /><summary type="html">Beautiful day for taking a ride on the Katsura (Oi) River to watch the cherry blossoms.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R04109.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Cherry Blossom Season・桜の季節</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210326/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Cherry Blossom Season・桜の季節 " /><published>2021-03-26T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-26T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/arashiyama</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210326/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
The sakura are in full bloom now, both on Mt. Arashi as well as along the river. A beautiful day to be out in a boat surrounded by cherry blossoms.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
現在、嵐山と川沿いに桜が満開です。 桜に囲まれた船に乗るのは最高の日和です。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Katsura River" /><summary type="html">The sakura are in full bloom now, both on Mt. Arashi as well as along the river. A beautiful day to be out in a boat surrounded by cherry blossoms.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R03967.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Egetsu Island・円月島</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210325/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Egetsu Island・円月島" /><published>2021-03-25T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-25T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/engetsu</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210325/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Sun sets over Engetsu Island in the beach town of Shirahama.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
白浜町の円月島の夕日。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Sunset" /><summary type="html">Sun sets over Engetsu Island in the beach town of Shirahama.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R03899.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Nachi Falls・那智滝</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210324/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Nachi Falls・那智滝" /><published>2021-03-24T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-24T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/nachi-falls</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210324/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
